channel.description: Find help for OIN problems Click here to give feedback about this page Content Notes Target personas: WIC App Developer,Experienced IAM developer Description: The goal of this page is to give links to OIN related education courses, OIN support communites, sites where they need to talk to sales, etc. Why is this here?: - Internal workshop: When asked “What prevents developers from being successful on the OIN”, respondents answered: - How to ask for and receive help from OKta - Links to Okta Education classes
